text: Kentucky Route 135 (KY 135) is an state highway in Kentucky. It runs from U.S. Route 60 (US 60) in Burna to KY 91 in rural Crittenden County northwest of Marion via Carrsville and Tolu. Highway 135 is locally named Tolu-Carrsville Road. ==Major intersections== Baptist church at Hampton ==References== 0135 Kentucky Route 135 Kentucky Route 135
